### ===== Wallets =====

### Get All Wallets
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets

### Search Wallets
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets?balance=gt|0.2&order_name=currency&order_direction=1

### Create wallets
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "balance": 0,
    "currency": "USD"
}

### Get Wallet By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{walletId}}

### Update Wallet
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{walletId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": true
}

### Delete Wallet
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/wallets/dd7c55c7-82df-4987-b2e2-74466dd9b011

### ===== Top-Up Transactions =====

### Create Top-Up Transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{walletId}}/top-ups
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 100.50,
    "method": "CARD",
    "payment_provider_id": "stripe_123",
    "payment_transaction_id": "txn_abc123"
}

### Get Top-Up Transaction by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/top-ups/{{topUpId}}

### Get All Top-Up Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/top-ups

### Get Top-Up Transactions for Wallet
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{walletId}}/top-ups

### Update Top-Up Transaction
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/top-ups/{{topUpId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "COMPLETED",
    "completed_at": "2024-01-15T10:30:00"
}

### Delete Top-Up Transaction
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/top-ups/{{topUpId}}

