### ===== Test Scenarios =====

### Scenario: Complete Top-Up Flow
# 1. Create a wallet
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "balance": 0,
    "currency": "USD"
}

### 2. Create a top-up transaction for the wallet
# @name createTopUp
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{walletId}}/top-ups
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 50.00,
    "method": "BANK_TRANSFER",
    "payment_provider_id": "bank_001",
    "payment_transaction_id": "bt_123456"
}

### 3. Get the created top-up (use the ID from response)
# @name getTopUp
GET {{baseUrl}}/top-ups/{{$createTopUp.response.body.id}}

### 4. Update the top-up status to completed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/top-ups/{{$createTopUp.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### 5. Verify wallet balance was updated (this would require a wallet balance check endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{walletId}}

